Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Tirano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tomomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'm a year older than you. Morning, Trikela.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ryoko-chan. Morning, Sakko-chan, Mikage-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause your date is in London?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could go there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've never been there. If you're leaving, make sure to lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, what're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.. you see..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd run into you here. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of going over to the dinosaur exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur Exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go? Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda? Good thing you're around too. I'll take you along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a dinosaur exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you two lucky to get to see dinosaurs with my commentaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that all three of us bumped into each other, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi and I didn't bump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two.. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you two were planning to go with me from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, you've got something wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, what a good guy you are, not that your face is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll take your generosity. Let's go enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going. It'll get crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oy, Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? This fossil has quite clear shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make very good study material for my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean I can give away a paving stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you ask, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ammonite?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Younger Matsunaga? Glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him how rare fossil like this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe there's a fossil here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of precious fossils like this all over this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's, why don't you go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried everywhere else with no luck! That's why I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. I can't believe this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Younger Matsunaga, tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I can't let go of this paving stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, are there other fossils like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tons of them. The buildings around here are quite old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- There're numerous ancient romance all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsunaga, I already asked for other fossils.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stegosaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, animals like these were roaming all over in ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why the dinosaurs became extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause ice age began?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was because of massive tectonic activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither. The most popular theory now is a meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge meteor struck Earth, and dust from the impact covered the entire Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the temperature went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more interesting that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't adopt to the change in environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know so much about dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna date with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this. There was a bird like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've seen the memory of the fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm OK now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fossil's memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no limit to your power, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. Will get mad if I tell ya, that's interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they whispering about? Dammit... today's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be trick of our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta be. Or else, everybody else would have been in panic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. We saw something weird, but that's interesting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, wanna play "it" for height?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Tomomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that dinosaur...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that hatched from the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm OK. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did draw that out of fossil, so it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't even touch the egg. So I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know the limit of your power. Just about the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the summer game preliminary, do you think I can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes way! Yu will for sure. You don't have limit either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's not hide and seek, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, stop joking and come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yamagishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's around here. There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can find fossils in town too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apatosaurus. It used to be called brontosaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the most popular herbivorous specie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's it doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we the only ones who can see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like Yamagishi-kun's the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His excitement is flowing into us. I can feel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a type of telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why it appeared? Let's go ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask him? You can't talk to him, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think telepathy would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys standing there for? Come on, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to tell me what to do? Besides today's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun, let's go. Now that I heard his voice, I can't leave him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be around here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An amber? It's so pretty. Can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Naah, I've been selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty, isn't it? It's like a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Do you want this? You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK. I know even a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A better one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be looking for others. Humans aren't one of his kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. After all, dinosaurs died out before humans were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dinosaurs lived in the same time as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're lots of drawing of dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even ancient dolls that look like nothing but dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they died out before our time, how come early humans could make those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your treasure, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my secret. Keep it secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Let me swear for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll swear or we'll swallow thousand needles."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, you really know about dinosaurs, don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must be lonely. He's gotta be looking for others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, I just saw translucent dinosaur over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-kun noticed first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty, isn't it? I bet it's a fern from the same time as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he'd be very happy if we give him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, today's his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Birthday? Yamagishi, is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be heading for the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's horn must sound like others that he's never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've never noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could say bye to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them. Move it, Yamagishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tomomi-chan and Mikage-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye! Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-tachi, how did you get up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-kun, look. The dinosaur turned this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The foghorn of the light house. Was that you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's holding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank you. Wow, it's a fern leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I wanna remember about the dinosaur, I'll look at this fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see it once in awhile, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you two are welcome to see it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's no fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Typhoon's coming. I feel I can do anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show off psychic power to Kageura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna check Noda-kun's feeling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls:\N"Hurricane in Maiden's Heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going to start all over again in typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.22,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:12.51,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.85,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:19.06,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:35.70,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:39.00,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:52.51,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:58.94,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:05.99,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.74,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:15.66,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:21.08,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.13,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:27.59,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.68,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:34.05,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:25.57,credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ending Song\N"There has to be Both of Us"\N("Futarijanakya Dame Nano")\NBy Dio
